  tutorialText: {fileID: 0}
  tutorialMessages:
  - You've spent days wandering through darkness. Now, at the end of this abandoned
    tunnel, a city waits. Silent. Empty. Or perhaps not. No one knows what remains
    beyond these walls... or what already lurks inside.
  - 'A transmission reached you before the signal died. In ten days, a rescue helicopter
    will arrive at the extraction point. But there''s a condition: the fuel tank
    in this city must survive. If it falls, so do your chances of escape.'
  - You're not alone. Someone managed to stay alive here. He won't tell you everything
    yet, but he knows how to turn scrap into weapons, defenses, and machines built
    for survival. Earn his trust, and he may become your greatest ally.
  - The city hides more than abandoned streets. Supply crates are scattered throughout
    the area, untouched for years. Some contain valuable resources. Others may attract
    unwanted attention. Every discovery comes with a risk.
  - Daylight is your opportunity. Explore. Scavenge. Prepare. But when darkness falls,
    everything changes. The infected emerge from the shadows, and they will come
    for the fuel tank. Every night is a battle for survival.
  - You have ten days. Protect the fuel tank. Strengthen your defenses. Survive the
    nights. When the helicopter arrives, be ready... if you're still alive to hear
    it.
  messageDelay: 15
  fadeImage: {fileID: 0}
  fadeDuration: 2
  nextSceneName: MainScene
